        <div class="section">
            <h1>Contact Us</h1>
            <p>At Lobster Logic Solutions, we’re here to help your business navigate the ever-changing digital landscape. Whether you’re looking for a custom solution, need advice on a web or mobile application, or just want to learn more about how we can work together, we’d love to hear from you.</p>
        </div>
